{"tid":1418941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（街坊入）有狗要求搜身/查身份證，我地可以咁樣","createTime":"2019-08-05T22:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T22:28:58.000Z","uid":23574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"826138936521f01b6d2d811c0510c54305437dd6","tid":1418941,"uid":23574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:00:35.000Z","msg":"D狗淨係識得用呢兩招兇街坊既姐<br />\n<br />\n查身份證：<br />\n如果屋企附近範圍落街係唔使帶身份證<br />\n我地可以叫隻狗跟上屋企拎<br />\n當然返到屋企忽然發現張證喺身係無問題啦<br />\n無記性犯法呀？<br />\n<br />\n搜身：<br />\n我地有權要求去到警署先搜<br />\n返到去咪慢慢比佢搜<br />\n記住拍片紀錄過程<br />\n佢無權唔比你拍片保障自己<br />\n<br />\n呢兩點既目的係令到隻狗要跟你走<br />\n一人夾走一個<br />\n佢地狗既數目就會減少<br />\n又可以令佢地食屎狗兩邊走<br />\n各位可以參考下<br />\n一陣check埋條例post埋出黎比大家睇下<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"7b3887e0fa423f28530822ad319a12ba72f9451e","tid":1418941,"uid":188463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:01:01.000Z","msg":"深水埗街坊被捕經過!!!! 啲狗痴左線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418552\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418552</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔該睇一睇 <br />\n仲未搵到街坊係邊個狗屋"},{"pid":"4df210aced4f92fd51beca046b0f70ae3a9f4d76","tid":1418941,"uid":23574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u0Qj148.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu0Qj148.png&h=f6f7640e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葉謝鄧律師行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j1GfAp9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj1GfAp9.png&h=4be538c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58616100d3eda0f21460a47256ca596230ffdfaa","tid":1418941,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:23:35.000Z","msg":"做咩要比佢知住邊<br />\n法例唔係要用到盡既"},{"pid":"d7b6ece2c4f02042bfc762dc426e93ebaa1312d0","tid":1418941,"uid":23574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58616100d3eda0f21460a47256ca596230ffdfaa","tid":1418941,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s